{"TopicId":184154,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"[Prototype][1.7.x] EVA Info Pane [ v0.0.2 @ 2019-05-07 ]","CreatedByName":"cakepie","CreatedById":69278,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-01T08:37:45Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cakepie","CreatedById":69278,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-01T08:37:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022QAgbrBf.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/QAgbrBf.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:50px;font-weight:bold;font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;text-decoration:underline;\u0022\u003EEVA Info Pane\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003Ev0.0.2 @ 2019-05-07\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis mod is in a prototype stage. It currently only has very barebones functionality and may be somewhat buggy.\u003Cbr\u003E\nIt is nonetheless being offered for download as a pre-release as it may be of use even in its current embryonic state.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe final product will obviously be much more polished and configurable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003EPlease do not bother me with feature requests at this time.\u003C/b\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI have already planned this out mod thoroughly and have 3 pages of design notes to work through and implement.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n~ ~ ~ ~ ~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022nw6aGur.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nw6aGur.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n~ ~ ~ ~ ~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003E\nAcknowledgements\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/75857-xevilreeperx/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002275857\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/75857-xevilreeperx/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@xEvilReeperx\u003C/a\u003E for assistance with a crucial technical gotcha.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n~ ~ ~ ~ ~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003E\nLicense\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll rights reserved\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n~ ~ ~ ~ ~\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003E\nDownload\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/cake-pie/EVA-Info/releases/tag/v0.0.2\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003EEVA Info Pane v0.0.2\u003C/a\u003E for KSP 1.7.x\u003Cbr\u003E\n(probably backward compatible, I haven\u0027t checked)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003E\u003Cu\u003EDependencies:\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?showtopic=162509\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003ECommunity Trait Icons\u003C/a\u003E is required and must be obtained separately.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003E\u003Cu\u003EInstallation:\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nDelete older version, if any.\u003Cbr\u003E\nPlace contents of GameData into your installation\u0027s GameData folder.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003E\u003Cu\u003ESource:\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/b\u003E \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/cake-pie/EVA-Info\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGitHub\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cb\u003E\u003Cu\u003EChangelog:\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003E\nv0.0.2 ~ 2019-05-07 ~ KSP 1.7.x\nPrototype\n\nv0.0.1 ~ 2019-05-01 ~ KSP 1.7.x\nPrototype\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-08T06:49:30Z\u0022 title=\u002205/08/2019 06:49  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 8, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by cakepie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Ev0.0.2\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Beetlecat","CreatedById":92207,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-02T21:18:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny info about the Info Pane? Whatsitdo? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-03T01:33:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a suggestion or feature request so don\u0027t take me seriously but I just NEED to throw this out here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be epic if this mod presented an API for life support mods to tap into, and placed an extra icon above kerbals\u0027 heads. This icon could easily shift between many colors, or several icons could appear as various negative (or positive) statuses occurred. This would be most useful to habitation mods that do add many negative statuses like Kerbalism, Kerbal Health and \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Umbra Space Industries (a collection of mods)\u0022\u003EUSI\u003C/abbr\u003E.\u003Cspan\u003E You could then tell at a glance who ate the last of their snacks (or had their bathroom moment) and is on EVA too long, or who\u0027s been poisoned by space radiation or otherwise.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyone who has played \u003Cstrong\u003EThe Sims\u003C/strong\u003E will understand. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cakepie","CreatedById":69278,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-03T03:21:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI welcome interest / support, but seriously:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223591742\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184154\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556699865\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269278\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cakepie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/1/2019 at 1:37 AM, cakepie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ENot accepting feature requests at this time.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are a variety of reasons why that is specifically highlighted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRant:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI also clearly highlight that status is WIP and not feature-complete and no tech support is forthcoming at this time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy? Reasons include (but are not limited to):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Things are very much WIP, odds are that any bug report / enhancement request is already a known issue / unfinished implementation / planned feature.\u003Cbr\u003E\n2. I\u0027ve thought carefully about what I want the mod to accomplish. As a matter of courtesy, at least let me finish implementing my vision before passing critique or asking for stuff \u003Cem\u003Eyou\u003C/em\u003E want.\u003Cbr\u003E\n3. Although I am happy to share ongoing progress and functioning prototypes for folks savvy enough to use and benefit from them, my time is better spent on development than tech support / community management.\u003Cbr\u003E\n4. As long as this is still licensed AAR, prevents any issue arising over ownership of ideas. (This is similar to why some authors/artists of ongoing series insulate themselves from fan-created content.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223592479\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184154\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556847187\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167617\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JadeOfMaar\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, JadeOfMaar said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a suggestion or feature request...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is totally a feature request.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich is already on my design doc, and being carefully planned for in terms of API etc. And has actually been mentioned elsewhere so I can prove it.\u003Cbr\u003E\nNot that that\u0027s any promise of if/when the feature would actually arrive.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/yFXyzDH.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/yFXyzDH.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to keep the thread open so people can subscribe and be notified when I post updates or release newer prototypes.\u003Cbr\u003E\nPlease don\u0027t make me lock the thread.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-03T05:46:38Z\u0022 title=\u002205/03/2019 05:46  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 3, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by cakepie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Ephrasing\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ssd21345","CreatedById":146209,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-03T04:39:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think anyone in this thread has said you steal someone\u0027s idea... Btw how can I find the design doc/roadmap? Or we\u0027re not supposed to read it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-03T04:43:23Z\u0022 title=\u002205/03/2019 04:43  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 3, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by ssd21345\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JadeOfMaar","CreatedById":167617,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-03T04:40:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69278-cakepie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269278\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69278-cakepie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@cakepie\u003C/a\u003E Heh. Sorry. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E I did drop an explicit \u0022disclaimer\u0022 my post when I said \u0022so don\u0027t take me seriously,\u0022 \u003C/span\u003Ewith the hope that you would see that I was jesting. I know very well the situation of being bombed and irritated with feature requests. I\u0027m sorry if I legit angered you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s nice to know you have that kind of protection in place and well in advance for your ideas.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cakepie","CreatedById":69278,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-03T06:01:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223592528\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184154\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556858398\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146209\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ssd21345\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, ssd21345 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think anyone in this thread has said you steal someone\u0027s idea\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPoor choice of wording. What I meant is there is proof I have not only already thought of it but am way ahead in terms of considering how it needs to be architected and implemented and deployed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223592528\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184154\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221556858398\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146209\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ssd21345\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, ssd21345 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0how can I find the design doc/roadmap? Or we\u0027re not supposed to read it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is messy scrawlings on note paper I did over lunch. I can\u0027t be bothered to turn that into something presentable/legible, would rather use my time actually making the mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cakepie","CreatedById":69278,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T19:57:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nv0.0.2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s actually a pane for the icon now and kerbal level has been added.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nw6aGur.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nw6aGur.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003E\nv\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E0.0.2 ~ 2019-05-07 ~ KSP 1.7.x\nPrototype\u003C/pre\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-07T20:44:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223595156\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184154\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557259039\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269278\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cakepie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n47 minutes ago, cakepie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nv0.0.2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere\u0027s actually a pane for the icon now and kerbal level has been added.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nw6aGur.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/nw6aGur.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode\u0022\u003E\n\nv\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E0.0.2 ~ 2019-05-07 ~ KSP 1.7.x\nPrototype\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntrying. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jesusthebird","CreatedById":176735,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-10T18:33:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like this idea!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-15T03:09:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69278-cakepie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269278\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69278-cakepie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@cakepie\u003C/a\u003Elove this little modlet. Have an idea to extend it: how about a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E indicator (either just the number and/or a fuel gauge) for the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E propellant?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}